                Mr. C. R. Attlee  (Walthamstow, West)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-acf13dea-8dc5-4dae-9172-0f4bee69d76a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-07-29/debates/bd0afc95-fa44-4729-92fa-82da4766779d/SuezCanalZoneBase(Anglo-EgyptianAgreement)#contribution-acf13dea-8dc5-4dae-9172-0f4bee69d76a">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
