                Captain Charles Waterhouse  (Leicester, South-East)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-19e10344-046a-4a1f-a579-2955c7c6f4f5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-07-29/debates/bd0afc95-fa44-4729-92fa-82da4766779d/SuezCanalZoneBase(Anglo-EgyptianAgreement)#contribution-19e10344-046a-4a1f-a579-2955c7c6f4f5">
