    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Does the hon. Gentleman say that we had the right?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1787a497-15b5-4841-98cd-285980ce4637" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
