        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I said nothing of the sort. What I asked was what we should do if Egypt went Communist.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-828bdacd-6e7c-48ae-b653-2dcb3806e44f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-07-29/debates/bd0afc95-fa44-4729-92fa-82da4766779d/SuezCanalZoneBase(Anglo-EgyptianAgreement)#contribution-828bdacd-6e7c-48ae-b653-2dcb3806e44f">
